OL,3,CPlaque unveiled for Britain's first
OL,4,Cblack professional footballer
OL,6,FTim Scott reports from the unveiling
OL,7,Fof the plaque at Deepdale Stadium
OL,9,FA plaque has been unveiled to honour
OL,10,Fthe country's first ever black
OL,11,Fprofessional footballer outside of his
OL,12,Fclub.
OL,14,FIt was unveiled at Deepdale Stadium,
OL,15,Fover 150 years after Arthur Wharton
OL,16,Fbegan playing for in 1886.
