OL,3,CPlaque unveiled for Britain's first
OL,4,Cblack professional footballer
OL,6,FThe plaque joins a statue and a mural
OL,7,Fthat were made to honour Arthur's
OL,8,Fcontribution to the sport. His great-
OL,9,Fgreat-grandson, Liam Rooney, says the
OL,10,Fplaque is another welcome tribute.
OL,12,FLiam said: "It's fantastic to see the
OL,13,Feffort people are putting in to keep
OL,14,FArthur's name relevant and still in
OL,15,Fpeople's minds."
