OL,3,CPlaque unveiled for Britain's first
OL,4,Cblack professional footballer
OL,6,FEarlier on in that same tournament, he
OL,7,Fwas described by Athletic News as "one
OL,8,Fof the best exhibitions of goalkeeping
OL,9,FI have seen for a long time."
OL,11,FIn 2020, a mural was unveiled in
OL,12,FDarlington on Arthur Wharton's 155th
OL,13,Fbirthday.
OL,15,FShaun Campbell, from the Arthur
OL,16,FWharton Foundation, said: "At long
OL,17,Flast I don't have to call for these
OL,18,Fthings, people are doing it
OL,19,Fthemselves. For this to come from the
OL,20,Fclub is just a wonderful thing."
